something that you have to

00:00:53.490 --> 00:00:54.560
stay on top of.

00:00:54.560 --> 00:00:57.000
People get this idea, like,
oh, I'll clean my desk off

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.250
once, and it'll stay perfect.

00:00:58.250 --> 00:00:59.940
It's a constant battle.

00:00:59.940 --> 00:01:01.830
SALLY HORCHOW: Well, now, I
