00:02:38.500 --> 00:02:39.410
somewhere out of the way.

00:02:39.410 --> 00:02:41.060
SALLY HORCHOW: So should I start
this whole process in

00:02:41.060 --> 00:02:43.360
the file cabinets then
and not on the desk?

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:44.420
TRACY MC CUBBIN: I would.

00:02:44.420 --> 00:02:44.750
I would.

