00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:08.510
I have a shredder, but I have
this bag of stuff to shred.

00:03:08.510 --> 00:03:09.010
TRACY MC CUBBIN: OK.

00:03:09.010 --> 00:03:11.470
So this is a great example of
what we talked about earlier

00:03:11.470 --> 00:03:12.790
