00:03:12.790 --> 00:03:15.810
I always tell my clients, open
your mail over your shredder.

00:03:15.810 --> 00:03:17.100
So shred it right away.

00:03:17.100 --> 00:03:19.210
And then what will happen
is this won't build up.

00:03:19.210 --> 00:03:20.940
We won't hit that tipping
point of you're

00:03:20.940 --> 00:03:22.160
